HEADWORD: Sanicle
<hw>San"i*cle</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., from L.
<ets>sanare</ets> to heal.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Any plant of
the umbelliferous genus <gen>Sanicula</gen>, reputed to have healing
powers.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

